text: Carl Benner is an electrical engineer at the Texas Engineering Experiment Station in College Station, Texas. He was named a Fellow of the Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers (IEEE) in 2014 for his contributions to the development of waveform-based analytics for electric power distribution. == References == Category:Fellow Members of the IEEE Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
